{"tid":1674243,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[國際民宣] 點Stand with Hong Kong? 杯葛中國！","createTime":"2019-10-25T06:11:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T18:03:33.000Z","uid":229411,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ed4efd7d138f92f84dab92b76e75a9c4fa5819af","tid":1674243,"uid":229411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T06:11:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Fight for Freedom, Boycott China!<br />\nFight for Freedom, Stand with Hong Kong</span><br />\n<br />\n有人話外國人唔知點stand with Hong Kong, 答案好簡單，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">逢中必反，杯葛中國</span></span>。既然香港罷買成功，就要叫埋外國人罷買中國貨啦。大至大型基建，小至日用品，都要會對<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中國貨</span></span>產生一種<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不信任</span></span>同埋<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">反感</span></span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國嘅華為電話、電腦就唔使講，仲有小米都係比較入屋嘅品牌，抄muji抄到出哂面嘅miniso，都要幫佢地宣傳吓啲仆街嘢。<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">其實中國嘅黑心食品除咗東亞國家知之外，世界仲有好多國家無報。係時候要宣傳吓</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國呢幾年最興叫人買佢嘅5G同高鐵，好多國家會貪平幫襯，借埋錢俾你起，結果可以參考斯理蘭卡同印尼高鐵。著名youtuber Naz Daily 都有提過 <a href=\"https://youtu.be/s1j_n6s2PFM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fs1j_n6s2PFM&d=r5q0VKZH5TKX5M4XK8oFTS1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=51231964\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/s1j_n6s2PFM</a><br />\n<br />\n民宣可以<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">提醒返外國朋友留意自己國家有無受中國大白象工程影響</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n起咗嘅要check返有無超支、偷工減料、貨不對辦問題; <br />\n起緊嘅就要查有無爛尾超支、貪污圍標之類問題; <br />\n未起就要諗清楚係咪伏，會唔會係另一個Money Trap。<br />\n<br />\n5G亦係另一個中國想可以搶嘅市場。呢個可以用<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">個人資料私隱</span></span>嘅方向打擊。Big data年代中國一定會想拎到全世界嘅數據，國家機密，甚至係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">每一個人電話嘅鏡頭同收音咪</span></span>。所以提醒返外國朋友，你會唔會想俾獨裁魔頭，例如 希特拉、蘇聯、北韓掌握你個人資料，一舉一動？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成個目的就係要喚醒外國人對中國有更多批判性思考，加上中國賣假嘢形象已經深入民心，成件事係合情合理。<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人反抗！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a64b701e4565f82adc8397184d0be5b5ecc2af6f","tid":1674243,"uid":229411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T06:11:42.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"9cebf78a99921e2a359c072731d913afa8b30d7f","tid":1674243,"uid":229411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T06:11:57.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"abb1fa6caf91a93f04e6f7fdc15075c1c2aa4fa0","tid":1674243,"uid":229411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T06:12:08.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"bd2f8075bb98dc63695c3cd72c58eb55c07f3c3a","tid":1674243,"uid":229411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T06:12:20.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"3ad0935fe1a9b398aa0513ac9f05fe5ecf26e24c","tid":1674243,"uid":229411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T06:12:33.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"2266f3c9fbf138904ffcfe2925dc0dfadb109cfc","tid":1674243,"uid":229411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T06:12:47.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"20c23e8c15b62e590700911988af992547cd27e9","tid":1674243,"uid":229411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T06:12:57.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"c5a28c033969548fa8562cf0e63edda8abb3185b","tid":1674243,"uid":229411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T06:13:08.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"193ad04665c5a528173912d5157f855e7924ca68","tid":1674243,"uid":229411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T06:13:19.000Z","msg":"